# mixipos-lander — environment example
#
# This is a fully static Astro site; it needs NO secrets to build or deploy.
# The only optional setting is a Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID.
#
# Analytics is intentionally OMITTED from the shipped HTML. To enable it,
# uncomment the placeholder gtag block in src/pages/index.astro and replace
# the placeholder id (G-XXXXXXXXXX) with the value below. Never commit a real id
# that belongs to another property.
#
# PUBLIC_GA4_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
